snippet.title: Leshy [PC] Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Leshy is a hack'n'slash game based in the near future, in which the player takes the role of a forest guardian from the Slavic mythology.

More details here: https://worthplaying.com/game/15705-leshy/

Leshy is in development for PC (Steam), scheduled for 2023.
